■ Simple step-by-step instructions guide you through everyday first aid scenarios.
■ Fully integrated with emergency numbers (such as 911) so you can call for help from the app at any time, even while traveling across borders.
■ Videos  learning first aid fun and easy.
■ Safety tips for everything, from severe winter weather to hurricanes, earthquakes and tornadoes help you prepare for emergencies.
■ Preloaded content means you have instant access to all safety information at any time, even without cellular or WiFi connection.
■ Interactive quizzes allow you to earn badges that you can share with your friends and share your lifesaving knowledge.

Special feature in location finder :

If you are searching for an free android app which you help you to
finding out many nearest places based on their category then you are in right places.

If you searching for restaurants near you, or good food near you, or may be you are searching for fancy restaurants near you but you actually 
don't know where they are then Location Finder will be your buddy.

Main Feature Of Location Finder:
# Support to use from any part of the world;
# Show all nearest places as a list;
# Showing details of a place;
# Showing places original photo;
# Showing places availability (if the place is OPEN or CLOSE);
# Showing the real review and rating which has been given by the real user;
# Showing latitude and longitude of the place;
# Showing phone number of the desire place owner;
# Showing website of the desire place;
# Can browse the website from the app. No need for any extra browser;
